videos.description: Parker Van Dyke drives to the paint and delivers the extra pass to David Collette for a layup, capping a 7-0 run for Utah.
videos.headline: Van Dyke's nice pass caps a 7-0 Utah run

videos.description: Paul White delivers a dime to a cutting Victor Bailey Jr. for an emphatic dunk.
videos.headline: Oregon's Bailey Jr. cuts to the rim for one-handed flush

videos.description: David Collette fakes the handoff and drives to the rim for a flush.
videos.headline: Collette catches Oregon sleeping for dunk

videos.description: Elijah Brown sinks a contested corner 3-pointer, his sixth of the game.
videos.headline: Oregon's Brown drains 6th 3-pointer

videos.description: Justin Bibbins gets to the paint and feeds David Collette with a bounce pass for a two-handed drunk.
videos.headline: Utah's Collette throws down crowd-pleasing slam

videos.description: MiKyle McIntosh absorbs the contact and manages to get the shot high off the glass for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Oregon's McIntosh makes tough and-1 bucket
